wikipedia_page.main: Natasha Howard (born 3 September 1980 in Harare) is a British rower. She rowed in the women's eight at the 2008 Summer Olympics but could not row in the finals due to illness. She is a graduate of the University of East Anglia and also studied at the University of British Columbia.
